Gideon Emery https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gideon_Emery 0 Gideon Emery (born 12 September 1972) is a British actor, singer and voice actor. He is best known for his recurring role Deucalion in Teen Wolf and for providing voice-over work in video games, television series and films.
